{"word":"G749 - ἀρχιερεύς - archiereús - ar-khee-er-yuce' - Chief priest","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀρχιερεύς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">archiereús</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ar-khee-er-yuce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Chief priest</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிரதான ஆசாரியர் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"chief priest, high priest"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G746 - ἀρχή - archḗ - ar-khay'/746\">G746</a> and <a href=\"#/G2409 - ἱερεύς - hiereús - hee-er-yooce'/2409\">G2409</a>; the <i>high priest</i> (literally of the Jews, typically Christ); by extension a <i>chief priest:</i> - chief (high) priest, chief of the priests.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1494/1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G2405/2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406/2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407/2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409/2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411/2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412/2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413/2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416/2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417/2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2418/2418\">G2418</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420/2420\">G2420</a>, <a href=\"#/G749/749\">G749</a>"}]}